{"tid":2154848,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"東網體育：「綠帽」唔止可以引發社會動盪、大國對立，亦會摧毀一支球隊嘅夢想","createTime":"2020-08-13T11:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T12:47:50.000Z","uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b74058e56c6d94c82a18b72a25437f3268b0ce16","tid":2154848,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:07:33.000Z","msg":"又係綠帽惹的禍 阿特蘭大出局因少咗佢<br />\n08月13日(四) 09:00<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20200813/bkn-20200813090000217-0813_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20200813%2Fbkn-20200813090000217-0813_00882_001.html&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzrCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=f4e1623e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20200813/bkn-20200813090000217-0813_00882_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n阿特蘭大喺歐聯8強悲壯出局，令好多球迷感到可惜，呢支意甲神奇球隊近年極速冒起，中場靈魂人物伊利錫居功厥偉，但呢位32歲斯洛文尼亞國腳因為疑似「戴綠帽」，自7月11日對祖雲達斯後，一直「人間蒸發」，以「私人原因」缺陣，令到球隊缺少1位進攻大將，為今場輸波埋下伏線。<br />\n伊利錫3年前由費倫天拿加盟阿特蘭大之後，成為球隊崛起嘅骨幹人物，上季意甲入11球，協助阿特蘭大取得歐聯入場券。佢今季表現更加出色，踢26場意甲攻入15球，創出職業生涯單季最多入球紀錄。<br />\n阿特蘭大今屆歐聯16強對華倫西亞，伊利錫兩回合合共轟入對手5球，包括次回合上演「大四喜」。聞戰鼓思良將，眼見阿特蘭大今場只差一步就可以晉級，令人更加懷念伊利錫。<br />\n當然世界上冇如果，但相信如果伊利錫今場在陣，賽果將會完全唔同。<span class=\"red\">「綠帽」造成嘅蝴蝶效應，唔止可以引發社會動盪、大國對立，亦會摧毀一支球隊嘅夢想。</span>"},{"pid":"dc396ef3e319332b4617a15d8c000fa5caf1be7b","tid":2154848,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:08:07.000Z","msg":"【東體爭議】阿特蘭大奇迹可一不可再<br />\n02月18日(二)<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20200218/photo/bkn-20200218170645767-0218_00882_001_01p.jpg?20200218180251\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20200218%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200218170645767-0218_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20200218180251&h=b7c64239&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歐聯16強首回合周中開打，其中周四(20日)凌晨就有阿特蘭大主場對華倫西亞，呢場波本來戲碼一般，但因為「歐聯初哥」阿特蘭大喺頭4場分組賽只有1分情況下，竟然爆冷出線，為意甲爭番些少面子，而成為「一時佳話」。未知是否受「燈神效應」影響，阿特蘭大今場竟然要讓半一，主W得1.62倍，簡直當西甲勁旅華倫西亞冇到，但可以話畀大家知，阿特蘭大奇迹可一不可再。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc59df4011d489909e3217c766a5872477cf6d5","tid":2154848,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:08:44.000Z","msg":"東網體育：為6000亡魂而戰！阿特蘭大要將歡笑帶回家<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2153126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2153126</a><br />\n<br />\n東網體育：阿特蘭大靈魂難鬥PSG 仲點創造奇迹呀<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2153881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2153881</a>"},{"pid":"9f1a9cb931efa298c7343609838c50c0e1fd7891","tid":2154848,"uid":36724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:09:06.000Z","msg":"東方反了反了"},{"pid":"95994b3892ad869797733d12573bcb5986bec1d7","tid":2154848,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:11:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzrCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=f3ceafb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網<br />\n有冇咁邪！阿特蘭大真係贏到PSG？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzrCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=f3ceafb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網<br />\n麥巴比提早復操鬥阿特蘭大有機上陣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzrCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=f3ceafb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網<br />\n鬥讓冠？阿特蘭大12碼都唔入又失分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzrCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=f3ceafb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網<br />\n阿特蘭大11連勝網民：捧埋歐聯冠軍啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzrCEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=f3ceafb1\" data-auto-link targ